\n    algorithm = 1,\n    n.start = 10,\n    n.iter = 10,\n    random.seed = 0,\n)\n\n\n\nsaveRDS(seurat_obj, 'seurat.rds')\n```\n\n**Environment:**\n- Fresh Galaxy installation\n- R 4.3.3\n- reticulate 1.43.0\n- Seurat 5.0","files":null}]}